## Architecture

- **Ensemble**: SVM + Logistic Regression + Passive Aggressive (soft voting)
- **Features**: TF-IDF (50K, trigrams) + handcrafted stylistic features (CAPS ratio, sensational words, exclamation count)
- **Confidence Tiers**: HIGH (>90%) / MEDIUM (75-90%) / LOW (60-75%) / UNCERTAIN (<60% or margin <20%)
- **Rules Engine**: Regex patterns catch obvious fakes instantly
- **Red Flags**: Sensational word count, CAPS ratio, exclamation frequency boost fake probability

